This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with image synthesis and quality evaluation. The use of Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs) also suggests that it could belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) category. The paper also involves the use of an ontology, which suggests that it could belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) category. The text description and conditioning of the generated image suggest that it could belong to the Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) category. Finally, the use of fashion images suggests that it could belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) category.
